    AppController, SchedulerController) to improve architecture.
  * Move tray lifecycle and log aggregation into AppController.
  * Deduplicate SchedInfo — config.h now re-exports schedcatalog.h.

 -- HM. Wassim <hmwassim95@gmail.com>  Sat, 18 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0200

scx-switcher (1.1.3) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Fix PrivOps kill()+start() reentrancy — async kill followed by immediate
    start() was a silent no-op when the old process hadn't been reaped yet;
    the second operation was never executed but its callback fired with the
    killed process's results. Pending operations are now queued and drained
    on the finished signal.
  * Add startup check that scxctl PATH resolution matches the PolKit policy
    exec.path (/usr/bin/scxctl). Warns in the log pane on mismatch instead
    of silently triggering a generic admin-auth prompt on every operation.
  * Fix errorOccurred(FailedToStart) not clearing a queued pending operation
    — the pending callback would fire with stale results from the wrong op.
  * Remove misleading comments in PrivOps about Qt suppressing finished
    signals (the old code relied on undefined behaviour).
  * Add scxctl policy-path verification to CMakeLists APP_VERSION (1.1.3).
  * Document why Qt6::Network is needed (QLocalServer/QLocalSocket for
    single-instance guard).
  * Fix install.sh shellcheck warnings (unquoted ${ARCH} in glob patterns).

 -- HM. Wassim <hmwassim95@gmail.com>  Tue, 07 Jul 2026 11:09:12 +0100

