scx-switcher (1.1.1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Fix writeConfig() using humanizeMode() for TOML values — "Low Latency"
    and "Power Save" are display strings; config.toml requires "LowLatency"
    and "PowerSave". Scheduler mode was silently wrong on boot persistence.
  * Fix fd leak in single-instance handler — newConnection never called
    nextPendingConnection(), accumulating open sockets on every second launch.
  * Fix PrivOps::run() silently dropping in-flight callbacks — only fired
    the old callback if m_configContent was set (writeConfig path). Regular
    operation callbacks were silently dropped. Extracted cancelInFlight().
  * Remove broken marquee — split logic produced garbled text; status text
    never exceeds threshold in practice; timer ran even when window was hidden.
    Replaced with plain setText(), which is correct and costs nothing.
  * Fix build-deb.sh — dpkg-buildpackage writes to ../; was looking in
    ./build/. Added -b flag (binary-only; skips unnecessary source tarball).
  * Fix install.sh — doubled "Launch:" and "Log saved to:" messages at end;
    step 4 printed "[DRY-RUN]" prefix inside a non-dry-run branch; missing
    ok() calls in steps 4 and 5.
  * Add libgl-dev to debian/control Build-Depends (present in install.sh
    but missing from control file, causing build failures in clean chroots).
  * Remove trailing commas from last Depends line in debian/control.
  * Remove data/com.scx-switcher.policy — stale old file using deprecated
    PolicyKit DTD; correct policy is in policies/com.scx-switcher.policy.
  * Remove generated debian/ build artefacts from repository
    (debhelper-build-stamp, files, *.substvars, *.debhelper.log).
  * Rename cleanup() to cancelInFlight() in PrivOps — clearer intent.
  * Remove config.h include from privops.h — not needed in the header.

 -- HM. Wassim <hmwassim95@gmail.com>  Sat, 13 Jun 2026 12:00:00 +0000

scx-switcher (1.1.0) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Merge best of both refactored codebases into unified scx-switcher.
  * Replace m_ignorePersist with QSignalBlocker for re-entrancy safety.
  * Replace temp-file + cp with pkexec tee + stdin pipe (fixes TOCTOU race).
  * Extract magic numbers into named constants.
  * Fix unused-parameter warning in ScxUtils error handler.
  * Remove stale includes.
  * Replace double hash lookup with constFind in humanizeSched().
  * Replace O(n) linear scan with O(1) static hash in onSchedChanged().
  * Fix font family case ("Monospace" → "monospace").
  * Add qWarning on saveState write failure.
  * Add atomic rename for saveState (temp file + rename).
  * Add 30-second timeout + errorOccurred handler to privileged operations.
  * Add query timeout to ScxUtils to prevent queue stalling.

